Subject: [experiment] ESM4 face rig render-buffer audit

Status: experiment, not queued in patches/openmw/series.
Depends-on: 0006-esm4-live-rig-bounds-telemetry.patch.
Depends-on: 0007-esm4-part-matrix-runtime-audit-gate.patch.
Proof baseline: run/proof-harness-sweeps/20260707-215634.
Proof result: run/proof-harness-sweeps/20260707-223752.

The face drawable audit reported rigged Fallout head meshes as source-valid but
render-invalid because the logger only inspected osg::Geometry drawables. For
SceneUtil::RigGeometry drawables, inspect the last-frame render geometry buffer
and emit a renderSource field so the proof ledger can distinguish a true empty
head from an uninspectable rig buffer.

The 20260707-223752 proof result made `faceAttachmentStatus=pass` for FO3 and
FNV current-mode actor slices. Visual proof still failed because actors remained
inverted/disassembled, so the next source slice must target actor
root/bind/controller basis instead of head render-buffer presence.

This patch is measurement-only and does not change rendering, skinning, actor
placement, or animation binding.

diff --git a/apps/openmw/mwrender/esm4npcanimation.cpp b/apps/openmw/mwrender/esm4npcanimation.cpp
--- a/apps/openmw/mwrender/esm4npcanimation.cpp
+++ b/apps/openmw/mwrender/esm4npcanimation.cpp
@@ -4445,6 +4445,22 @@ namespace MWRender
 
             return geometry->getVertexArray()->getNumElements();
         }
 
+        osg::BoundingBox computeFalloutGeometryBounds(const osg::Geometry* geometry)
+        {
+            osg::BoundingBox box;
+            if (geometry == nullptr)
+                return box;
+
+            box = geometry->getBoundingBox();
+            if (box.valid())
+                return box;
+
+            const osg::Vec3Array* vertices = dynamic_cast<const osg::Vec3Array*>(geometry->getVertexArray());
+            if (vertices == nullptr)
+                return box;
+            for (const osg::Vec3f& vertex : *vertices)
+                box.expandBy(vertex);
+            return box;
+        }
+
         class FalloutFaceDrawableAuditVisitor : public osg::NodeVisitor
         {
         public:
